data.description: RARE find, 3 bedroom in desirable Windstone Crossing.  Oversized master with adjacent full bathroom and laundry room, offers plenty of storage space.  Spacious Living room features fireplace with gas logs.  Vaulted / cathedral ceilings, Separate front door entrance, Glass sliding rear door that leads to gorgeous stamped concrete patio.    Interior photos coming soon.  Sellers in the process of packing, however if you don't mind the boxes, come visit before it is gone.  Furniture also available for sale.
